{"tid":975752,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"分手一個月了，我還是不敢清理我們的遺物，你的所有東西仍在，不是我懶，而是我不捨得，我不像你","createTime":"2019-01-10T01:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T10:43:36.000Z","uid":171816,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"da10272c6b88ed40f2a15a7b2eb74f29bed618f2","tid":975752,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DctjJOs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDctjJOs.png&h=fc54cb47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚長情好慘慘豬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係得班港女先會buy<br />\n男人老狗係到靠慘情劣鳩上位<br />\n真係影撚衰哂 過兩日又去溝過第二件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a4ce28f88635f92c29c7a8f899bcfba8037d45","tid":975752,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"那段情跟牆一樣慢慢地脫落了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdda96d28bdeb467bc90ee68c81d20b826edb08","tid":975752,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99a4ce28f88635f92c29c7a8f899bcfba8037d45","tid":975752,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"那段情跟牆一樣慢慢地脫落了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> eason"},{"pid":"607efb5aa3125facae6b459e923609014cea0ea6","tid":975752,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"凌晨時在地上　排列你與我未有處理那碎片<br />\n將戲飛一堆　安靜看下去　我又怎麼可眼淺<br />\n牆櫃藏著舊物　留下了線索　落泊還如何避免<br />\n給我多一刻　一直掛念你　我便能遺忘昨天<br />\n<br />\n一串冰冷的鎖匙　沒人用誰還在意<br />\n一隻灰暗的指環　誰要留念　留念至此<br />\n<br />\n＊殘缺的一地雜物　代表一對愛人<br />\n　前程以至照片　撕開了兩份<br />\n　來吧趁亂想時　投進垃圾箱　除掉腐敗氣氛<br />\n　連同當晚信念　拋開得勇敢<br />\n　拿手機清洗　過去的興奮<br />\n　無人留得低你　我怎麼要自困<br />\n<br />\n荒廢的半張空床　沒人睡誰還在看<br />\n苦澀的半杯清茶　能夠緩慢　緩慢喝光<br />\n<br />\nRｅｐｅａｔ　＊<br />\n<br />\n可銷毀一件襯衫一盞吊燈<br />\n可肢解一本破書一對木櫈<br />\n可清空一部電腦幾張唱片<br />\n還剩餘二十萬樣紀念品<br />\n<br />\n連同當晚信念　拋開得勇敢<br />\n殘忍的清洗　過去的興奮<br />\n無人留得低你　我怎麼還自憐地逐日去等<br />\n為何回首卻發現　即使怎夠狠<br />\n無形虛空的　卻始終很近<br />\n如何才可捨棄　腦袋中那烙印<br />\n如何才可捨棄　半空中罪咎感<br />\n如何才可捨棄　你給的那藥癮"},{"pid":"9c15d91dde8f01a7ff7f480360cc1deac64c3744","tid":975752,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:15:33.000Z","msg":"遺物？！"},{"pid":"e197d4529746309c247df0f3e173d4c9a5cd7732","tid":975752,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"其實男人係咪都鍾意扮情聖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcba461f5d4402d2ff9efbf90142a82be524af89","tid":975752,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"死撚咗先會叫遺物"},{"pid":"6be7b5c5d4e17accf7b8003e02537e22c1f1ccf5","tid":975752,"uid":225846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"你點cap到咁低清？"},{"pid":"6f7a8f40efc189ee31c45b39b6b87dc0f9167844","tid":975752,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e197d4529746309c247df0f3e173d4c9a5cd7732","tid":975752,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"其實男人係咪都鍾意扮情聖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:13:12.000Z","msg":"港女buy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把囡囡安慰"},{"pid":"cf5ea6733cec001f88be5adceb7660403053d0e5","tid":975752,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be7b5c5d4e17accf7b8003e02537e22c1f1ccf5","tid":975752,"uid":225846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"你點cap到咁低清？"},"citedBy":0,"re